---
title: Sticky Beef and Broccoli Bowls with Buttery Rice and Garlicky Veggies
description: Level up your dinner game with this sticky beef and broccoli bowl! Tender beef coated in a sweet and savory glaze pairs perfectly with crisp broccoli, rice, and crunchy cabbage. An Asian-inspired twist that brings bold, satisfying flavours to your table!

